FBIS3-60113 "jptdd003__l94079" JPRS-TDD-94-003-L Document Type:JPRS Document Title:Narcotics 19 January 1994 WEST EUROPE TURKEY Narcotics Teams Seize 31 Kg of Heroin in Istanbul TA0801205194 Ankara ANATOLIA in English 1520 GMT 7 Jan 94 TA0801205194 Ankara ANATOLIA Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Istanbul, Dec.7 (AA) -- In an operation here, narcotic teams have seized 31 kilos heroin. Five persons were detained in relation to the narcotic. A statement by the narcotics department of the Security Directorate said today that, teams acting on a tip-off, carried out an operation to the home of Aziz Celik in the Gungoren district of Istanbul. The narcotic was found in Celik's home. His interrogation led to the seizure of Makhial Altan, Kamil Yakut, Celimhan Capa and Naif Bayhan. Investigation into the case is expanded.
